47be-9544-b413384aeabf"],

Cell["\<\
Using agentic LLM is a strange experience, but not an altogether bad one. It \
can offload a lot of low-level programmatic drudgery. Things that are humanly \
possible but time-consuming can be done in significantly less time now. \
Occasionally the LLM will go completely off the rails and pursue an incorrect \
solution. It helps to monitor the progress and abort the process when this \
happens. An LLM can easily spend a large budget of tokens on doing something \
completely wrong or inefficient. But overall I like this new mode of \
programming, especially because it makes it much simpler to do complex things \
at a speed that is 100x the speed of my human typing and thinking.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.985870296642593*^9, 
  3.985870617763918*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a74d7ba-1640-4257-9977-\
6abe1cd06624"]
}, Open  ]]
},
